get blogs of user "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
=================================================================

NAME
----

get blogs of user - Get the blogs a user belongs to.

SYNOPSIS
--------

Get the blogs a user belongs to.

PARAMETERS
----------

 `$user_id` 
:   ([*integer*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Integer "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) User ID
    Default: *None*

 `$all` 
:   ([*boolean*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Boolean "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Whether to retrieve all blogs, or only blogs that are
    not marked as deleted, archived, or spam.
    Default: false

RETURNS
-------

 `` `(array)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   A list of the user's blogs. False if the user was not found or an
    empty array if the user has no blogs.

CHANGE LOG
----------

Since: 3.0.0

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`get_blogs_of_user()` is located in `wp-includes/user.php`.

